================================================================================

Theoretical Foundation
================================================================================

The Supply Economy architecture is based on Promise Theory by Mark Burgess.
Promise Theory is an academic framework — it is not software and carries no
software license. Its principles are applied here as an architectural pattern
for autonomous service coordination.

Reference: "Promise Theory: Principles and Applications" by Mark Burgess
